# nomenclatures
- Use camelcase for simple files (like utils, etc ...)
- Use PascalCase form components

# For next js
- If a component needs of user interaction, consider that as client component
- Uses the server components whenever possible
- Use TDD
- Use the SOLID principles
- Use the KISS (Keep it simple stuipd) method
- For branchs, always create branch as feat/bugfix/hotfix followed the commit lint pattern